snippet.title: The Sims™ 2 H&M Fashion Stuff Official Trailer
snippet.description: Must-have fashions for your Sims from H&M! Rule the runway with all new fashions inspired by H&M and build your own retail store with all new retail items. Get more info at www.TheSims2.com.
